<HEAD>Aome U.S. Enterprises Succeed in Japan, Chamber Official Says</HEAD>
<HEAD>EDS: SUBS 2nd graf to CORRECT spelling of McDonald's and SUBS last
graf to show trade deficit billion, sted million</HEAD>
